column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.dered_u as u,p.dered_g as g,p.dered_r as r,p.dered_i as i,p.dered_z as z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, s. zErr as d_redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.class=&&&  AND g-r BETWEEN # AND #   AND u-g BETWEEN # AND #   AND r BETWEEN # AND #  AND u BETWEEN # AND #  AND g BETWEEN # AND #
